Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[in English] What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a service entrance here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,bartenders and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mm-hmm.\N- I'm thinking cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uh-huh.\N- Like a living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, flowers\Neverywhere, low booths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already bought\Nall the liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you afford all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? I save.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been saving for,\Nlike, two fucking years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The builders say it'll\Nbe ready in a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's happening, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need to make a\Nprofit, like, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I know I can\Nwith the right team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, you know how\Nmuch I make at Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus Duke kind of\Nleaves me alone, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know that\Nwhatever we're making,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke's making a shit ton more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sleazy owners. I\Nwon't be a sleazy owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll raise your weekly salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus 25% of commissions\Nand up sells.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be ours. I\Ncan't do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look, Sam, I'm... I'm sorry.\N- Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But a new business...\NToo much risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much... Luna, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Sam, if you want to be a\Nmama-san, just be a mama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is your problem?\N- I am not judging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's just...\N- You're judging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How does your boyfriend\Nfit into all this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he Chihara-kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he won't\Nexpect his cut
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or take over completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we keep our work and\Npersonal life separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know by now\Nthat's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- By now?\N- Am I missing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[muffled dance music]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- [whispering]\N- Pol, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? We miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're feeling your\Nabsence tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get your hot\NSlavic ass down here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps approaching]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's new with the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Luna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you'd offer her a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'll think\Nabout it. We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- You okay?\N- Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pol hasn't answered\Nher phone all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't show up to\Nwork. I called Miralina
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and they said that\Nthey haven't seen her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,since last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she wants to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes people\Nneed time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mm, I don't know.\N- It's not like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[meat sizzling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[moaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese] Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake, it's getting\Nharder and harder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to get a hold of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out with a source right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, listen, have you\Nheard anything about Tozawa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,being formally charged?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about Katagiri\Nhaving new evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Evidence? What evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I'll ask around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you know the suspect\Nwho was brought in yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Kaori Shoda murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- I need you to go out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to confirm the information\Nabout the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a\Nbigger story here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,connecting this case
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to the others I've\Nbeen tracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[moans]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[upbeat music]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Josh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Josh Adelstein, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave Fisch from Rock bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, come here,\Ncome here, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you look different, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Seeing the sights.\N- Taking in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No shit? Doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For a Japanese newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy shit. Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's amazing.\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you okay?\N- You look a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm having a bad\Nblow fish hallucination
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or if you're actually\Nstanding in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this will\Nclear the cobwebs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Anything you can\Ndo, I can do better ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ I can do anything\Nbetter than you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- ♪ No, you can't ♪\N- ♪ Yes, I can ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- ♪ No, you can't ♪\N- ♪ Yes, I can ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ No, you can't no, you can't ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Yes, I can yes, I can ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I was there.\N- Right? Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still the best\NFrank Butler I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- I gotta go.\N- I gotta get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, yeah, yeah, totally.\N- Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get you my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me tonight. My\Nhotel has a great bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay.\N- I might be busy working, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cool, cool.\N- Got it, got it, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- But it was great to see you.\N- Great to see you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Bruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I know Kung-fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[all laughing and jeering]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really haven't seen her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,since Friday morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I caught her trying to\Npack my Pradas for a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- A trip?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She was going away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Going away?\N- With... with who? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, aren't you guys, like,\Nbest mates or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shouldn't you know?\N- You live with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just stop by long enough\Nto pack up some clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause my guy's a pilot, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Awesome.\N- She's left all her stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.03,0:24:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.21,0:24:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Pol?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.22,0:24:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who are we talking about?\N- Polina.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.44,0:24:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.36,0:24:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the fuck is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.52,0:24:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I can keep track
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.94,0:24:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of every girl in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.53,0:24:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, I'm worried.\N- I haven't seen her
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in four days, and you\Nshould be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.41,0:24:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's gonna pay for your\Nshit designer clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.66,0:25:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.96,0:25:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[mocking chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Police said that she filed
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.68,0:25:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,three complaints\Nagainst her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.05,0:25:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them were filed, none\Nof them were followed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.97,0:25:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he murdered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.68,0:25:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.68,0:25:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that together\Nwith the other women,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.52,0:25:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that paints a really\Nnasty picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.52,0:25:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, each case I look\Ninto fits a pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.36,0:25:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The police ignore warning signs
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.49,0:25:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and young women\Nare getting killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is front-page stuff.\NCan you make deadline?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.11,0:25:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.41,0:25:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you heard anything\Nelse about the Tozawa thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.70,0:25:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Jake, it's not\Na priority right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.21,0:25:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have to go.\N- We just have to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.46,0:25:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if he got charged...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.06,0:26:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone buzzing]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.94,0:26:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.26,0:26:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.26,0:26:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.15,0:27:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.18,0:28:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[somber music]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.18,0:28:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.08,0:28:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.17,0:28:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone buzzing]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.68,0:28:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.93,0:29:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.38,0:30:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[lounge music]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.17,0:30:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.51,0:30:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[singing in Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.64,0:30:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.96,0:31:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[murmured greetings]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.23,0:31:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[applause]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.55,0:32:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[applause]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.49,0:32:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.05,0:32:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[applause]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.60,0:33:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[lounge music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.64,0:33:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.99,0:33:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[singing in Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.08,0:33:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.70,0:34:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[both laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.71,0:34:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Marvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.04,0:34:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right,\Nright, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.29,0:34:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He dropped some serious\Nknowledge on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.21,0:34:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things\Nthat he taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.92,0:34:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that I still use\Nat my job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.71,0:34:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Long time ago.\N- We're getting old, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.67,0:34:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.67,0:34:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you come to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.38,0:34:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought I'd take a year off\Nbefore grad school at Mizzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.60,0:34:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, get some\Nlife experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.10,0:34:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And this place has\Nblown my mind, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.89,0:34:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean, Tokyo,\Nright? It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.02,0:34:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not Missouri.\N- Not Missouri. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.57,0:34:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank fuck for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.44,0:34:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank fuck for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.82,0:34:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So how's your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.91,0:34:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think they're good.\N- You know, I don't really have
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.66,0:34:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,much time to check\Nin these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.25,0:34:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm busy with work, but...\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.50,0:34:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that, like,\Nyour sister was
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.58,0:34:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of some, like,\Nheavy treatments, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.92,0:34:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.30,0:34:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[upbeat country music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.17,0:35:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I mean, it's Columbia,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.34,0:35:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so people talk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.51,0:35:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,People should keep their\Nfucking mouths shut
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.10,0:35:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,about shit they\Ndon't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.02,0:35:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.52,0:35:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Jessica's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.73,0:35:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're keeping in touch
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.23,0:35:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's... she's better\Nnow. She's healthy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.11,0:35:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.11,0:35:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Saturday night and\Nthe moon is out ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.91,0:35:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ I'm gonna head on over\Nto the twist and shout ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.20,0:35:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Find a two-step partner\Nand a Cajun beat ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.62,0:35:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ When it lifts me up,\NI'm gonna find my feet ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.75,0:35:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.96,0:35:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to see the\Ncoolest place in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.46,0:35:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.71,0:35:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[electronic pop music]
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.51,0:35:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.72,0:35:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.85,0:35:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.19,0:35:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.65,0:35:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Muy bueno, my man.\N- Muy fucking bueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.94,0:36:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to grab that\Nbooth over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.28,0:36:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get a couple drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you on\Nthe dance floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.36,0:36:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.72,0:36:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.49,0:36:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.49,0:36:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need one?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.20,0:36:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you were followed\Neverywhere you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.04,0:36:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you on the dance floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.18,0:37:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Thought I was going\Nmad in a hurry ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.51,0:37:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Getting' stressed, makin'\Nexcess mess in darkness ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.89,0:37:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ No electricity ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.06,0:37:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Something's all over\Nme, greasy, insomnia ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.73,0:37:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.24,0:37:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, ne, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.59,0:37:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.05,0:37:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.77,0:37:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.82,0:38:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby, let him talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.01,0:38:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You fucking piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.13,0:38:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who got her in that\Ndebt, huh? It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.14,0:38:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey.\N- Motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.70,0:39:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.08,0:39:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to find out\Nwhat she knows or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.17,0:39:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.70,0:39:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.35,0:42:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.02,0:42:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.52,0:42:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Half a day from\Nhere in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.35,0:42:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- When's she back?\N- Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.02,0:42:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, baby, go back\Nand ask when soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.36,0:42:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you running\Naway from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.69,0:42:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know whose men\Nare in there right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.82,0:42:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tozawa's.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.69,0:42:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how much\Ntrouble I could get in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.95,0:42:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- for stirring things up?\N- Baby, I am worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.03,0:42:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.53,0:42:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.37,0:42:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can barely look\Nme in the eye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.12,0:42:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you need\Nsomething, I am your baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.29,0:42:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.08,0:42:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know exactly what\NI'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.29,0:42:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has been the\Nsame since that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.42,0:42:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You pull away when\NI reach for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.13,0:42:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, I don't.\N- Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.63,0:42:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.35,0:42:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't about us.\NShe's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.05,0:42:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.39,0:42:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.06,0:42:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I do\Nhas consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.06,0:42:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now this is\Nfucking interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.44,0:42:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you are making\Nthis about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.40,0:42:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you beat the\Nshit out of people
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.74,0:42:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,for your boss, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.82,0:43:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... that's\Nfine. That's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.41,0:43:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I need something,\Nwhen I need help,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.37,0:43:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's for me,\Nthere's consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.45,0:43:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you. I thought\Nyou were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.54,0:43:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not different.\NYou're a thug.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.54,0:43:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.75,0:43:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiring girls to cheat lonely\Nmen out of their salary?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.30,0:43:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call that? A pimp?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.05,0:43:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.22,0:43:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not forcing\Nanyone to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.30,0:43:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And no one forced Polina.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.56,0:43:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.81,0:43:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dangerous world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.11,0:43:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,People get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.11,0:43:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.28,0:43:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.21,0:43:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[electronic dance music]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.96,0:44:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.36,0:44:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is awesome, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.59,0:45:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[upbeat music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.67,0:45:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.81,0:45:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[singing in Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.77,0:45:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[speaking Japanese]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.23,0:45:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.93,0:46:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans quietly]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.10,0:46:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.11,0:46:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[audio distorting]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.70,0:46:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[guests exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.62,0:46:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.13,0:46:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.34,0:46:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.64,0:46:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing\Nbefore, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.22,0:46:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a model for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.48,0:46:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you were real good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.56,0:47:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Flattery will get you nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.82,0:47:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that how you two met?\N- When you were modeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.86,0:47:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think\NI'm going to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.53,0:47:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with you about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.33,0:47:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking about your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.62,0:47:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interested in you. I\Nwant to know about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.66,0:47:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[upbeat music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.71,0:47:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.67,0:47:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say he\Ncame along at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.21,0:47:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when modeling was becoming\Nless interesting to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.18,0:47:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.48,0:47:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.28,0:47:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ominous music]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.28,0:48:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.59,0:48:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.34,0:48:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hey, get your\Nfucking hands off her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.72,0:48:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave... Dave, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.56,0:48:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Onegaishimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.33,0:48:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.51,0:48:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... ah, shit,\Nare you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.22,0:48:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, man, I'm fine.\N- Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.68,0:49:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on.\N- Let's get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.68,0:49:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.63,0:50:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The second to last fucking page.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.17,0:50:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[soft music]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.22,0:50:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.10,0:50:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You spelled it out beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.27,0:50:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And that story would\Nhave opened a lot of eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.06,0:50:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,if they hadn't\Nfucking buried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.48,0:50:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm glad you think so.\N- Maybe next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.91,0:50:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.87,0:50:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm starting to not see
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.04,0:50:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the fucking point of\Nany of this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.04,0:50:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake, I do it despite\Nthe indifference
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.84,0:50:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because somebody has\Nto tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.55,0:51:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to build a wall\Nof information brick by brick,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.55,0:51:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,story by story,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.89,0:51:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,until the facts\Ncannot be ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.85,0:51:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then things have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.73,0:51:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't they?\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.67,0:51:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.46,0:51:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.18,0:51:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
